data.description: Welcome to this light, bright and airy colonial located on a quiet cul de sac in North Stafford!  The main level has durable engineered wood flooring.  There is a formal living area/study area in the front and a large yet cozy family room off the kitchen.  The kitchen has lovely 42" cabinets , granite counters, a double sink, beautiful tile backsplash, very large chef's island and gas cooking!  The large dining area off the kitchen is appointed with crown and chair molding.  The family room walks out to a large screened porch with ceiling fan and private, well landscaped fenced yard.  The upper level includes 4 generous bedrooms including the master suite with vaulted ceilings and master bath with ceramic tile flooring and walk-in shower.  The hall bath also has tile flooring and tub surround.  The lower level recreation room features a lovely powder room, built-in bar with Kegerator, bar furniture, custom sized pool table and electric fireplace. Front loading washer and dryer are included in the ample laundry area.  The large 2 car garage has built-in ceiling storage and a lawn irrigation system.   Conveniently located close to shopping, I-95 and Quantico!
